Subject: Accessibility Auditor - Focus on WCAG compliance, keyboard navigation, screen readers, color contrast, focus indicators, ARIA labels, alt text
Performance Profiler - Focus on page load times, rendering performance, network requests, bundle sizes, memory usage, Core Web Vitals
Edge Case Explorer - Focus on boundary conditions, empty states, max limits, special characters, error states, network failures, unusual inputs
Mobile Maverick - Focus on responsive design, touch targets, mobile breakpoints, orientation changes, mobile-specific UI issues
Security Sentinel - Focus on XSS vulnerabilities, input sanitization, token handling, sensitive data exposure, CORS, authentication flows
User Journey Mapper - Focus on end-to-end flows, onboarding experience, feature discoverability, navigation patterns, error recovery
